  GO criteria for redoing the full pipeline on Base:
    1. Oracle label class_balance covers >=3 classes, no class >70%
    2. Predictor val gain_over_majority > 0 (anything positive)
    3. Eval ours-oracle tokens_per_second OR accuracy differs from adablock
         by a margin big enough to publish (>=2 pts acc or >=2 t/s)
  NO-GO criteria (stick with Instruct results, write paper as-is):
    1. Oracle labels collapse to 1-2 classes
    2. Eval still shows identical accuracy across schedulers
